<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubearogfrostborn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bearog Frostborn</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>knows that Warriors are Superior</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>53</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>5/11/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>6:13:40 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Question on fine plate vs crafted prices.</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial"><br>
Not sure about prices an ye server, but as a younger warrior I harvested HQ Bear skins ta afford me armor. On karana they go for 30pp each and bronze is 1 or 2pp per AC point. I's killin bears fer days ta get them hides. I had the brabed armplates as well when I was a wee laddie. Willowwhisps be a fine source O income as well. I would add here that I began makin most O me monies by buyin and sellin for dark races outta Halas. I'd go to da camp, take their orders and plat, hike back across the frost to Halas and buy. Made a tidy profit doing that. In me mid seasons I did work for three different guilds during a guild war. I was a mercenary, I had participated in several wars before. Then at 16th season I was hailed by a rep from one of these 3 new guilds, all we're seasoned 12 and below. They paid me plat ta war with them against the other. I turned that into an occupation for a while but wearin that many guild tags had an adverse affect in finding a decent guild later.<br>
<br>
Yer equipment sounds inline and good fer yer season. I agree with Jaikar, jagged bands are a good upgrade to be had on the cheap. Crafted prices on me server are at a low to be sure, bracers down to or under 100pp, where as FP is still at 10pp per point of AC. Dunno why but it is. Ye'll also find EB BP going for 900 to 1k.<br>
Nonetheless young warrior, methinks yer doin well. Put yer worrior'in abilities ta work and make 'em lands twixt Freeport and Kith safer fer the travlers.<br>
<br>
